    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle and take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Trim, then chop your<strong> green beans</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1635255706818-x200.jpg",
