    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky Spanish-style chicken & rice </strong>and drizzle the<strong> lemon aioli </strong>all over</p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong> and a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
